  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nIf you are in a channel, then go to another section, when you receive a mention or a normal message in that channel, the badge either doesn't show or disappears immediately (and the channel is marked as read I think)\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Go to a public chat\r\n2. Open your profile\r\n3. Unfocus the app (eg go into another Desktop app)\r\n4. In another account, mention the first user in the channel he's in\r\n\r\nResult: a badge appears and disappears or just doesn't appear.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nThe badge should show, because even though it was the last active channel, it is not currently active.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: 0.9.0RC1\r\n\r\n",
